For this project, I have used the **Electron.js stack** for building a **desktop application**.  

### 🌐 **Full Tech Stack:**  
- **JavaScript/Node.js** – Core language for app logic.  
- **Electron.js** – Framework for cross-platform desktop apps using web technologies.  
- **HTML/CSS** – For the user interface.  
- **VS Code** – Development environment.  

### 🖥️ **Stack Name:**
**Electron + Node.js + JavaScript (ENJ)** — or simply **Electron.js stack**.  

This gives you a clean, modern, and cross-platform desktop app. 🎯